      "description": "Looking for a cheap runabout, first project, or something to get you from A to B without spending a fortune? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, budget-friendly option with plenty of potential for the right person. It\u2019s got the usual wear you\u2019d expect and would suit someone practical who values affordability over showroom looks. If you want a straightforward car at a sensible price, this could be a great little buy.",
